# {{projectName}}

Performance test suite built with [Gatling](https://gatling.io/) using Java.

## Prerequisites

- Java {{toolVersions.java}}+
- Maven 3.9+

## Quick Start

```bash
# Run the default load simulation
mvn gatling:test

# Run a specific simulation
mvn gatling:test -Dgatling.simulationClass={{javaPackage}}.simulations.LoadSimulation

# Run stress test
mvn gatling:test -Dgatling.simulationClass={{javaPackage}}.simulations.StressSimulation
```

## Reports

After a test run, Gatling generates an HTML report in `target/gatling/`.
Open `index.html` in your browser to view detailed results.

Target URL: `{{baseUrl}}`

